About us:
Nestled in the heart of historic Downtown Starke, FL., The Downtown Grill is more than just a restaurant - it's a local gathering place where good food, great company, and unforgettable memories come together.
Locally owned and operated, we pride ourselves on offering American Contemporary Cuisine in a warm, inviting atmosphere.  Whether you're joining us for a family dinner, catching up with friends at our full-service bar, or just stopping by for a freshly cooked meal, you'll feel right at home.
Looking for a little friendly competition?  Our Trivia Nights, hosted by David Rodgers, bring the community together for laughter, learning, and a whole lot of fun.  Trivia Nights are every Thursday at 7pm and it's FREE to play!  We also have our Bingo with Lynn on Wednesdays at 7pm for our Bingo enthusiasts.  It's very interactive and a whole lot of fun, plus it's FREE to play as well!!
Planning a celebration, meeting, or special event?  We've got you covered with our spacious banquet/event room, private booking options, and a dedicated full-service catering team ready to bring the flavor and fun wherever you are!
At The Downtown Grill, we're deeply rooted in our community values - proudly family oriented, and community driven.  From our kitchen to your table, every dish and experience is crafted with care.
We can't wait to see you here and share a piece of
#ThatGrillLife
with you!!

photoswipe markup
Root element of PhotoSwipe. Must have class pswp.
Background of PhotoSwipe. 
         It's a separate element as animating opacity is faster than rgba().
Slides wrapper with overflow:hidden.
Container that holds slides. 
            PhotoSwipe keeps only 3 of them in the DOM to save memory.
            Don't modify these 3 pswp__item elements, data is added later on.
Default (PhotoSwipeUI_Default) interface on top of sliding area. Can be changed.
Controls are self-explanatory. Order can be changed.
